.SH "NAME"
keepalived \- load\-balancing and high\-availability service

.SH "SYNOPSIS"
\fBkeepalived\fP
[\fB\-f\fP|\fB\-\-use\-file\fP=FILE]
[\fB\-P\fP|\fB\-\-vrrp\fP]
